    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK35">
<l>aḻukkā ṟavāvekuḷi yiṉṉāccoṉ ṉāṉku</l>
<l>miḻukkā viyaṉṟa taṟam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dharma is what goes about shunning four things:</l>
<l>envy, jealousy, hate and bitter words.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
